# Core

- Read `AGENTS.md`, [governance.mdc](governance.mdc), and the active goal in `docs/07-backlog/goals.md` before coding.
- Respect `docs/02-product/mvp-scope.md` — do not build out-of-scope features without a new goal.
- **Only execute `ready` goals** — see goal state machine in [governance.mdc](governance.mdc).
- Smallest correct diff; no drive-by refactors; stay within goal **Touch map**.
- Follow [security.mdc](security.mdc) — no secrets in repo; no prod commands without human approval.
- Follow project tone and safety constraints in product/architecture docs.
